divs: Sighting DetailsWe saw one blinking light from the sky. I asked my friend if it's an airplane since it is weird that the light was orange. Then she said no, maybe it's a helicopter. Then I said that helicopters don't fly that high. Then as we were staring at it, it suddenly slowed down and stopped. Then it ascended and then it is gone. Then a second light appeared from where the first light came from.
Summary: The blinking and path pattern and size and speed were inconsistent
